snippet.title: Development Report 3 - ALPHA GAMEPLAY SHOWCASE + 2 NEW INDIVIDUALS? | YASUKE: A Lost Descendant
snippet.description:
Delve deeper into the gameplay of that is 'YASUKE: A Lost Descendant' with our first Alpha showcasing.
Rebuilt from the ground up using Unreal Engine 5, here's a sneak peek as to what's to come from us in the future...

What's this, two new individuals enter the world of YASUKE both friend...and foe.
